### Get Post by ID (paste from Create Post response)
GET http://localhost:3000/post/<POST_ID>

### Update Post
PUT http://localhost:3000/post/<POST_ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": "u123",
  "title": "Hello updated",
  "content": "Updated content"
}

### Create Comment (use same POST_ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "<POST_ID>",
  "senderId": "u777",
  "message": "Nice post!"
}

### Get Comments for a Specific Post
GET http://localhost:3000/post/<POST_ID>/comments

### Get All Comments
GET http://localhost:3000/comments